column4: I've got this big problem with outkafe and ubuntu 64 libraries http://forum.ubuntu-it.org/index.php?topic=83945.0
you have a libs problem; the libraries you have are 64bits while the application is 32bits
thanks. is there a way to fix it ?
you need to have the 32bits libraries. ubuntu has /lib32 and /usr/lib32 for that
